  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a wok or large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add minced garlic and red pepper flakes. Sauté for about 30 seconds until fragrant.",
    "Pour in lemon juice while stirring continuously to avoid burning.",
    "Toss in halved green olives, sliced almonds, and finely diced onion. Stir-fry for another minute or so.",
    "Garnish with chopped parsley before serving.",
    "Serve immediately as a side dish or main course."
